<Defaults>
   <Button color="#282828" textColor="#F0F0F0" fontSize="18"/>
   <Text color="#F0F0F0"/>
   <Image preserveAspect="true"/>
</Defaults>

<Button id="show-drawer" onClick="toggleDrawer"
  color="#00000000"
  width="85" height="75" offsetXY="200 -2"
  rectAlignment="UpperLeft"
  tooltip="Victory Point Salad controls">
  <Image image="vps drawer logo" width="100%"></Image>
</Button>

<Panel id="drawer"
  width="100" height="200"
  active="false"
  rectAlignment="UpperLeft"
  offsetXY="200 -75"
  childForceExpandWidth="false"
  showAnimation="Grow"
  hideAnimation="Shrink"
  animationDuration="0.25">
  <VerticalLayout padding="0 5 5 5" spacing="5">
    <Button id="clean-up" onClick="showNewGameDrawer"
      width="200">
      <Text>New Game</Text>
    </Button>
    <Button id="the-docks" onClick="theDocks"
      width="200">
      <Text>The Docks</Text>
    </Button>
  </VerticalLayout>
</Panel>


<Panel id="new-game-drawer"
  width="300" height="50"
  active="false"
  rectAlignment="UpperLeft"
  offsetXY="300 -100"
  showAnimation="Grow"
  hideAnimation="Shrink"
  animationDuration="0.25"
  >
  <HorizontalLayout padding="0 5 5 5" spacing="5">
    <Button id="new-1p-game" onClick="new1PGame" width="200">
      <Text>1 player</Text>
    </Button>
    <Button id="new-1p-game" onClick="new2PGame" width="200">
      <Text>2 player</Text>
    </Button>
    <Button id="new-1p-game" onClick="new3PGame" width="200">
      <Text>3 player</Text>
    </Button>
    <Button id="new-1p-game" onClick="new4PGame" width="200">
      <Text>4 player</Text>
    </Button>
  </HorizontalLayout>
</Panel>
LuaScript:
zone_special_deck_guid = '2992c4'
deck_special_guid = '1a44bd'
card_endgame_guid = 'e0fa97'
deck_midgame_guid = '9526fc'
deck_starter_guid = 'bc69b7'

in_the_box_guid = 'ca7e8a'
in_the_box_pos = { x = -21, y = 0.96, z = 1.8 }

special_deck_pos = { x = -13.1, y = 1.1, z = -6.3 }
special_spacing_x = 6.1

drop_height = 5

num_players = 2

next_round_button_params = {
  click_function = 'nextClicked',
  function_owner = self,
  label = 'Next Round',
  position = { x = -0.1, y = -0.3, z = -1 },
  rotation = {0,180,0},
  width = 650,
  height = 200,
  font_size = 100
}

new_game_params = {
  click_function = 'newGame',
  function_owner = self,
  label = 'New Game (2P)',
  position = { x = -0.1, y = -0.3, z = -1.5 },
  rotation = {0,180,0},
  width = 700,
  height = 200,
  font_size = 100
}

function onLoad()
  zone_special_deck = getObjectFromGUID(zone_special_deck_guid)
  zone_special_deck.createButton(next_round_button_params)
  zone_special_deck.createButton(new_game_params)
end

function nextClicked()
  deck_special = getObjectFromGUID(deck_special_guid)

  for i=1,num_players + 1 do
    deck_special.takeObject({
      position = {
        x = special_deck_pos.x + i * special_spacing_x,
        y = special_deck_pos.y + drop_height,
        z = special_deck_pos.z,
      },
      top      = true,
      flip     = true,
      smooth   = true,
    })
  end

end

-- hardcoded to 2p for now - but parameterize this!
function newGame(n)
  print(n)
  deck_special = getObjectFromGUID(deck_special_guid)
  deck_special.shuffle()
  card_endgame = getObjectFromGUID('e0fa97')

  deck_midgame = getObjectFromGUID(deck_midgame_guid)
  deck_midgame.shuffle()
  for i=1,5 do
    deck_midgame.takeObject({
      position = in_the_box_pos,
      top      = true,
      flip     = false,
      smooth   = true,
    })
  end

  deck_starter = getObjectFromGUID('bc69b7')
  card = deck_starter.deal(3, "Blue")
  card = deck_starter.deal(3, "Red")

  card_endgame.setPositionSmooth({
    x = special_deck_pos.x,
    y = special_deck_pos.y + 5,
    z = special_deck_pos.z,
  }, false, true)

  deck_midgame.setPositionSmooth({
    x = special_deck_pos.x,
    y = special_deck_pos.y + 10,
    z = special_deck_pos.z,
  }, false, true)

  deck_starter.setPositionSmooth({
    x = special_deck_pos.x,
    y = special_deck_pos.y + 15,
    z = special_deck_pos.z,
  }, false, true)

end

function toggleDrawer()
  if(UI.getAttribute('drawer', 'active') == "true") then
    UI.hide('drawer')
    UI.hide('new-game-drawer')
  else
    UI.show('drawer')
    UI.hide('new-game-drawer')
  end
end

function new1PGame() newGame(1) end
function new2PGame() newGame(2) end
function new3PGame() newGame(3) end
function new4PGame() newGame(4) end
function showNewGameDrawer() UI.show('new-game-drawer') end

ObjectStates.Description: Use this checker to find the coordinates on the table
ObjectStates.LuaScript:
self.setName("The Position Checker")
self.setDescription("Use this checker to find the coordinates on the table")
self.createButton({
  click_function = 'check_position',
  function_owner = self,
  label = 'Check',
  position = {0.1,0.23,2},
  rotation = {0,0,0},
  width = 500,
  height = 500,
  font_size = 100,
})

function check_position()
    pos = self.getPosition()
    pos_str = "{ x = "..pos[1]..", y = "..pos[2]..", z = "..pos[3].." }"
    broadcastToAll(pos_str)
    print(pos_str)
    setNotes(pos_str)
end
